OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777619131
OL,3,CRyanair calls for suspension of new EU
OL,4,Cairport checks
OL,6,FRyanair has called on EU governments
OL,7,Fto suspend new border checks which has
OL,8,Fcaused mayhem at some airports. The
OL,9,Fnew entry / exit rules have seen some
OL,10,FBritish passport holders face huge
OL,11,Fqueues, with some even missing their
OL,12,Fflights as a result, ITV News Consumer
OL,13,FEditor Chris Choi reports
OL,15,FThere are fears that May's bank
OL,16,Fholidays will see more airport queues
OL,17,Fas a result of the EU's new border
OL,18,Fscheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
