OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777619131
OL,3,CRyanair calls for suspension of new EU
OL,4,Cairport checks
OL,6,FThe Exit/Entry system, also known as
OL,7,FEES, requires travellers to register
OL,8,Ffinger prints and facial images at
OL,9,Fspecial kiosks.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Ryanair wrote to
OL,12,Fofficials across the region calling
OL,13,Ffor the system to be scrapped for the
OL,14,Fwhole summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
