CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777619131
OL,3,CRyanair calls for suspension of new EU
OL,4,Cairport checks
OL,6,FThe letter from Europe's biggest
OL,7,Fairline says: "Passengers are
OL,8,Fsuffering long passport control queues
OL,9,Fand in some cases missing their
OL,10,Fflights ...Ryanair has written to the
OL,11,Fgovernments across 29 EES countries
OL,12,Furging them to suspend EES until
OL,13,FSeptember."
OL,15,FTourism chiefs have been quick to
OL,16,Fsupport the Ryanair demands.
