OL,3,CRyanair calls for suspension of new EU
OL,4,Cairport checks
OL,6,FHelder Martins, President of the
OL,7,FAlgave Hoteliers Association told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "Sometimes the clients wait two
OL,9,For three hours, this is impossible
OL,10,Fbecause the flight took two hours and
OL,11,Fthen they wait two hours to come into
OL,12,Fthe Algarve.
OL,14,F"This is terrible and this is
OL,15,Fsomething that kills all the promotion
OL,16,Fthat we can do".
OL,18,FGreece has already halted the scheme
OL,19,Fat its airports until the autumn.
