PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777619131
OL,3,CRyanair calls for suspension of new EU
OL,4,Cairport checks
OL,6,FEuropean airports have warned of EES
OL,7,Fwaiting times up to two or three
OL,8,Fhours. Some experts predict four hour
OL,9,Fdelays.
OL,11,FAirports already have power to make
OL,12,Ftemporary suspensions of the EES, but
OL,13,FRyanair and others now want the scheme
OL,14,Fscrapped for the whole summer of 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
